title: 2 bed 1 bath
posting_body: ['Building refresh happening here!', 'Units are available immediately for Mid-August and September 1st.', 'Another available unit is a one bedroom renting for $900 a month.', 'New and newer appliances, including dishwasher, updated flooring and designer paint colors.', 'Now that warm weather is here we are excited to beautify the outside!', 'It will be a great match to all the new carpet in the hallways and entry spaces.', 'The building has a huge parking lot with a bike rack.', 'On site laundry.', 'Super close to the light rail and bus stop.', 'On-site caretaker.', 'Security cameras in parking lot and entry.', 'The on-ramp to I-94 is right down the road.', 'Pet rent $25 per/mo and $100 non-refundable pet deposit.', 'Parking lot parking $25 per/mo', 'Heat, water, and garbage included.', 'Each apartment has A/C unit.', 'Requirments:', 'Credit score: 600+ with no past due (co-signers accepted)', 'No evictions or felonies', 'This property no longer qualifies for sec 8.', 'All occupants need to be on the lease and all adults need to qualify.']
